{"tid":1467166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Sword Lam: 這是運動第二個輿論關口","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:08.000Z","uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"54aad7c319a8c5086d6a72b499cca55487f6475c","tid":1467166,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"這是運動第二個輿論關口。第一次是七一衝擊立法會，大家僥倖渡過了，沒有割席事件。<br />\n<br />\n今次是第二次。隨著運動的深入，愈多愈多不同的人會受牽連，阻人登機、圍堵敵軍，可能某程度走得太前，部分行動有改善空間。但如果香港人連這一步都跨不過，運動註定一事無成。<br />\n<br />\n2015年光復行動，捉住一對青關會母女，細路女大喊，泛民割席譴責，本土泛民自此勢成水火。歷史的教訓，大家還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n敵人無底線，我們不一定要跟著他們無底線。但當有隊友可能走得太前時，我們也要支援他們，拒絕任何負面的指摘。可以檢討，可以提改善建議，但that's all，請勿割席。<br />\n<br />\n記住，激進化的雞蛋，仍是雞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1074563587/posts/10216677018252578 s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1074563587%2Fposts%2F10216677018252578%20s%3D100001644574516%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=0af59709\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1074563587/posts/10216677018252578 s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"2dbf645fb1c631178602684ac94f527ac1871f89","tid":1467166,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1074563587/posts/10216677018252578?s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1074563587%2Fposts%2F10216677018252578%3Fs%3D100001644574516%26sfns%3Dmo&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=2b440f2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1074563587/posts/10216677018252578?s=100001644574516&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bd3a7a006761255a916ba57ea6da293e16a5edd5","tid":1467166,"uid":63184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b35cf339a144